<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title><para>A <tag>productionrecap</tag> is a cross-reference to a
      <tag>production</tag>.</para>

      <refsection><info><title>Processing expectations</title></info>
        

        <para>A <tag>productionrecap</tag> is rendered exactly like
        the production to which it refers. The purpose of the
        <tag>productionrecap</tag> element is to allow a
        <tag>productionset</tag> to contain copies of
        <tag>production</tag>s defined elsewhere. This frequently
        makes it easier for readers to <phrase role="keep-together">understand</phrase>.</para>
</refsection>

